The '''Derelkoos Desert''' was a desert on the planet [[Klatooine/Legends|Klatooine]]. It was notable for the [[Fountain of Ancients]], a naturally evolving glass sculpture revered as a holy site by the [[Klatooinian/Legends|Klatooinian]] people.<ref name="Galaxy Guide 12">''[[Galaxy Guide 12: Aliens — Enemies and Allies]]''</ref>

